# AuraBoot Performance Regression — example crontab entries
#
# To install: crontab -e  (then paste the relevant lines)
# To view:    crontab -l
#
# Required environment variables should be exported in the shell's profile
# or injected via a wrapper script:
#
#   BASE_URL=http://your-server:6443
#   PERF_BASELINE_DIR=/path/to/scripts/perf-ci/baseline
#   PERF_ALERT_WEBHOOK=https://hooks.slack.com/services/XXX/YYY/ZZZ
#   USERNAME=admin@auraboot.com
#   PASSWORD=Test2026x
#
# Replace /path/to with the absolute path to your AuraBoot checkout.

# Nightly perf smoke (2am local time) — fast, ~5 min
0 2 * * * /path/to/scripts/perf-ci/run-perf-regression.sh --profile smoke >> /var/log/perf-ci.log 2>&1

# Weekly full regression (Sunday 3am) — 3-run median per test, ~20 min
0 3 * * 0 /path/to/scripts/perf-ci/run-perf-regression.sh --profile full >> /var/log/perf-ci.log 2>&1
